  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Gnome&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Gnome Magic&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Some gnomes ally with capricious faerie dragons or share a supernatural kinship with these enigmatic creatures. Gnomes with this trait add 1 to the DCs of saves against the illusion spells they cast. Additionally, a gnome with a Charisma score of 11 or higher can use each of the following spell-like abilities once per day: <i>ghost sound</i>, <i>grease</i>, and <i>silent image</i>. The caster level for these effects is equal to the gnome's character level. The DC for these spells is equal to 10 + the spell's level + the gnome's Charisma modifier. This trait replaces gnome magic.  </p>",
